FR - Voici un nouveau concept de coopération : Find the Solution. Dans cette map, plusieurs salles se succèderont avec a l'intérieur de chacunes d'elles, une épreuve. Vous allez devoir trouver comment venir a bout de cette épreuve grâce aux éléments présents dans la salle, et a votre cervelle. Par exemple, vous disposez d'une grenade, au loin, vous apercevez une boite, il vous suffit de viser juste et de lancer la grenade dans la boite.

EN - This is a new cooperation concept : Find the Solution. In this map, there will be many rooms with a challenge to succeed. You will have to find how to finish all challenge. For exemple, you have a grenade, and you can see a box far away. So you have to put the grenade in the box.
Find the solution

This is a FootRace map. The goal of a FootRace map to reach the end before anyone else, even your teammates. The first to reach the end of this map will trigger explosions that will kill everyone else on the map. So race over fire, fans, lasers, and other dangerous obsticales in order to take out everyone else. Enjoy!


**The screenshots really don't do this map justice.**

This is an FR (FootRace) style map. It is Mario themed and you race over obsticals including mushrooms and fire to get to the flag at the end of the level. The first one to jump on the flag at the end is the winner and the other players (including your teammates) will meet an unfortunate end. In FR maps nobody is on the same team so feel free to push your buddies off those mushrooms!

This is the latest and greatest of my FR (FootRace) map's. The setting is a Greek temple in the sky, the home of the wind god. You have been summoned to fight to become his successor. You must race against others to the wind god's throne on the top of the temple. Once you reach the throne you will be given the god's divine powers and they will blow everyone else off the temple and back to Earth. On the way to the throne you will face many trials, traps, and illusions. If you have any trouble and get stuck on the map remember the illusion part of what I said. This map is truly different than anything you have ever played and I'm sure you will have fun racing against to become the next wind god. Please assess and enjoy this map. 


A special thanks to Drunkguitarist for many trap ideas and the idea for the theme. Also thanks to his girlfriend for correcting us and letting us know this is more Greek than Roman :D.

The aim of this map is to race against your team-mates and the opposing team to the castle. So first go through a swamp which slows you down then cross the bridge across the moat, but watch out for traps. Then first person to reach the top destroys everyones ropes and fall to their deaths. This FR is Footrace which is a new kind of map and are studio is currently making more.
